# System Architecture Overview

This system is an end-to-end AI-powered content pipeline built in n8n that automatically researches, writes, optimizes, and publishes SEO-ready blog articles to WordPress.

## Step 1: Article Discovery & Vector Storage
- Fetches fresh news or topic sources daily
- Saves articles into a vector store for semantic relevance matching
- Enables long-term memory and topic reuse

## Step 2: Relevance Scoring
- AI evaluates articles based on relevance and intent
- Filters low-quality or off-topic content
- Ensures only high-value topics proceed

## Step 3: Research & Enrichment
- Performs deep research using external sources
- Aggregates supporting data
- Prepares structured research summaries for writing

## Step 4: Article Writing & SEO Optimization
- Generates long-form blog content using AI
- Applies SEO structure (headings, keywords, internal logic)
- Prepares metadata for search engines

## Step 5: Media Generation & Publishing
- Generates or fetches images
- Uploads images to WordPress
- Creates and publishes the final blog post
- Sets metadata and publication status

## Key Design Decisions
- Modular step separation for maintainability
- AI quality gates before publishing
- Fully automated daily execution
- Human-readable outputs for easy review if needed

